entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Èske ou tcheke tout klib la?" t="Did you check the entire club?" b="" a=""/>

<kiroshi l="creo" o="Gade gwo chay manman sa... Li pa bèl je? Mwen te di ou mete tèt ansanm ak BARGHEST ta peye" t="Look at this motherlode… Ain't it a pretty sight? I told you teaming up with BARGHEST would pay off." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Pff, si ou di sa... Merde, choom, mwen pa t 'enskri pou okenn travayè depo…" t="Pff, if you say so… Shit, choom, I didn't sign up to be no warehouse worker..." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Sezi ou ka wè nenpòt bagay ak tèt ou nan bounda yo…" t="Surprised you can see anything with your head up their ass..." b="" a=""/>

<kiroshi l="creo" o="OK, jis nan ka mwen pral kache sig la anba yon lòt kouvèti ICE epi limen nouvo jwèt Calixte a." t="OK, then just in case I'll hide the sig under another layer of ICE and fire up Calixte's new toy." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Lli tout nèt.." t="Through and through." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Epi ou enstale pwotokòl sekirite ou te resevwa nan men Calixte?" t="And you installed the security protocol from Calixte?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Oke, non, men…" t="Well, no, but..." b="" a=""/>

<kiroshi l="creo" o="Fè li. Yon moun enpòtan pou BARGHEST dwe nan Kè Loutrè byen kout. Bezwen asire li pwòp." t="Do it. Someone important for BARGHEST is due at Heavy Hearts soon. Need to be sure its clean." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Mwen wè nou konprann youn lòt." t="I see we understand each other." b="" a=""/>
